{"tid":2024031,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"(攬炒懶人包) 全民拎綜援 政府冇銀用","createTime":"2020-05-19T11:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T11:44:13.000Z","uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"31163a581d63ce397aa79031f395c736073802dd","tid":2024031,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實搞非政府慈善組織籌款比義士生活可否扣稅?</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7einsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7einsy.png&h=775fd294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府冇銀用 一籌莫展<br />\n<br />\n用盡每一個方法駛政府錢拉挎政府財政，有機會/合資格拎綜援的人可以試下申請 唔駛再怕人嫌棄<br />\n<br />\n搞到政府冇錢先係攬炒主要目標，冇錢就冇能力推行反人權的政治理念<br />\n<br />\n(攬炒公務員)政府冇錢比人工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒國企藍店)永續黃圈 民主消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒銀行)唔夠美金 大陸金融有流動性陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒流動支付)唔用支付寶吸唔到香港人血<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒金融流動性)冇美金印唔到錢借唔到出去救經濟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒人民幣)數碼人民幣買唔到外國貨只能國內消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n(反攻香港)建立海外武裝反政兼逃生 養流亡義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒經濟)數碼經濟轉型 反送中生機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒外史)全球最大全民抗極權經驗 波蘭反共運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請每日推一次</span>"},{"pid":"8e1ef7f4d19a4a41eb4e25a1541d9542204b5d93","tid":2024031,"uid":277486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n六四晚會用網上直播有冇得諗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2023855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2023855</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74a5ea711ad84caa1a98cee3fccfcfb21f1b6622","tid":2024031,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要贏，就要大部分人不滿現狀，必須包括政府，不必令其不滿你，只要令其不滿自己</span>"}]}